  <div class="section-spacing">
    <div class="three-about-sections">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
            <h2>How it works</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <%= image_tag("icon_1.png", class: "icon-about") %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8">
              <div class="info">
                <h2>Discover</h2>
                <p>Create an account by clicking the sign up button below. Fill in all your basic information and lets get rolling.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <%= image_tag("icon_2.png", class: "icon-about") %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8">
              <div class="info">
                <h2>Search for projects</h2>
                <p>Create an account by clicking the sign up button below. Fill in all your basic information and get lets get rolling.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <%= image_tag("icon_3.png", class: "icon-about") %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8">
              <div class="info">
                <h2>Create an account</h2>
                <p>Create an account by clicking the sign up button below. Fill in all your basic information and get lets get rolling.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="homepage-what">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1 margin-top margin-bottom">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2>What do we do?</h2>
        <p>Maintaining a portfolio of your work has long been around for fields like tech and design. But for most other industries, the quality of your work often drowns out amongst crappy things like CVs, standardized tests, and who you know. We believe that people should first and foremost be judged on the quality of their work.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="homepage-sample">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <% @sample_projects.each do |project| %>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <%= render 'shared/card_open_project_full_imagery', project: project %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


